---
title: Vegan Maple Carrot Power Bowls with Turmeric-Toasted Couscous & Lemony Hummus
description: Maple syrup is the not-so-secret ingredient that makes tonight’s harissa-seasoned carrots so cravable. The sweet, tender carrots are served up bowl-style along with a variety of delightful flavors and textures: turmeric-seasoned couscous, garlicky kale crisps, creamy hummus, and a sprinkling of dried cranberries and walnuts. This dish will have you coming back for bite after bite!
